description:
On this 2023 retrospective episode of ANN International, Heroes: The Bible trivia game hits one million downloads, making a global impact on players' lives.

The evangelistic series 'Hope For Africa' results in one hundred thousand baptisms in Nairobi, Kenya. 

Also, ADRA leads $105 Million food resilience project in Congo, empowering communities for sustainable change.

Stay tuned as ANN brings you these captivating stories and provides coverage of other global news. For a deeper dive into these headlines and more, visit adventist.news.

ANN is the official news channel of the Seventh-day Adventist Church.
